1.4 million European Union carbon permits in separate auctions.  Germany sold 850,000 permits for December at 7.72 euros
($10.02) a metric ton on the European Energy Exchange AG,
according to data form the exchangeâ€™s  website . Greece sold
500,000 spot permits at 7.69 euros a ton on the Athex exchange,
